highlights.text: Eden Hason has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “לאהוב אותך כל יום” is the highest at #2.
“vampire” by Olivia Rodrigo is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #9.
“Cruel Summer” by Taylor Swift is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 50 spots at #114.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 278 weeks straight.
